title: 306: Way too early NFL Week 1 storylines
itunes:title: 306: Way too early NFL Week 1 storylines
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks compare the wild world of NBA free agency to the NFL's free agency frenzy (3:36). The guys then debate which divisional cellar-dweller will rise to the top in 2018 like last season's Eagles (8:48). DJ and Bucky then get pumped for the opening week of NFL & college football by going through each game and giving their favorite storyline to watch (29:22).
